            WRITTEN By F. T. Authour of the Supplement, to iustify certaine places, and authorities alleaged, as well by him in the said Supplement, as by the Cardinall in his Apology, and pretended to be answered by M. D. Andrewes.
            
            ALSO An Appendix touching a Register alleaged by M. Franc. Mason for the lawfull Ordayning of Protestant Bishops in Q. Elizabeths Raigne.
            
